name: No Thoughts, Head Empty (this.Lewashi();)
description:
You ever pulled up a state test, took one look at the first question, and thought about better times, or cats, or tiktoks...

Hop into a middle school mindspace and pull yourself together one scattered, dancing, rock-tossing braincell at a time.

Controls: Arrow Keys/Joystick To Move, Space/X To Jump, Hold X to SlowFall/Boost On Spring

Made in 2 Weeks For StraightUpGruntledGameJam#2
